snippet.title: Dragon Ball FighterZ - XB1/PS4/PC/SWITCH - Vegeta Character Intro
snippet.description:
The base Vegeta is joining Goku for the next DLC update of DRAGON BALL FIGHTERZ early August.
Discover his move set including his signature move: the Galick Gun and his Super and deadliest attack, the Galaxy Breaker.
